title: Wing Luke Museum Affiliated Area: Park Home
body: Step Into a Uniquely American Story  More than a museum, the Wing is an experience. A chance to truly understand what it was - and is - to be Asian American in the Pacific Northwest. Take a guided tour of a historic hotel and learn the inside story about what makes the local Chinatown-International District unique. Visitors explore thought-provoking exhibitions of real stories, including actor and martial arts master Bruce Lee.              Special Events   Explore both inside and outside our museum walls. The Chinatown-International District is an important part of historic Seattle.
